snippet.title: EVERING Chapter I - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
EVERING Chapter I: Journey of a Tale is OUT!

BUY THE GAME ON ITCH https://purpurest.itch.io/evering (Free demo!)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Evering is an episodic RPG with an epic story, traditional turn-based combat and a cute pixel art style. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Follow us on Twitter https://twitter.com/PurpureSt_
Talk to us by joining our Discord https://discord.gg/KNV83JXWjp
Support us further on Ko-fi https://ko-fi.com/purpurestudio

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Music: 
“A Fight un the Field”
“Thoughts” 
Composed by Jonathan Shaw (www.jshaw.co.uk)
